{
  "stem": "6777.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sometimes I just went out to be out, to make the impression that you go, that you don't always stick around.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After those bandits came, we arranged for another-- for another safe house, where my friends from the resistance lived.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Vera, Mina, and Eva, the three, they went over there, got new Kennkarten.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And grandma and I, we stayed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they changed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They changed, And grandma and I, we stayed in the flat to see what happens.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, the mail just came in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Never mind.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a few days later-- two days later, not just a few-- just two days later, the same bandits-- I've been coming back from the market, and they found me and put a gun to my back and led me back to the flat.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I had not been going there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Just before the flat-- the entrance to the flat on the right-hand side-- there was a German [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I've been walking in front with a gun to the back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when I came to the German [NON-ENGLISH], I didn't go forward, but I jumped to the side.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the man did fire the gun.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Germans from the [NON-ENGLISH] came out to see what's happening.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I told them, there was a man who went shooting me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And why would they want to shoot you?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so-- and finally, they've taken my grandmother and myself into the Aleja Szucha.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was the Gestapo headquarters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they said, you reported the bandits came there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "With my grandmother, who only spoke German and couldn't speak well Polish and with myself, we reported our incident, not saying that we've been suspected of being Jewish or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
